Class TypedFallbackCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dyn4j.collision.narrowphase.AbstractFallbackCondition

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class TypedFallbackCondition
extends AbstractFallbackCondition
implements FallbackCondition, java.lang.Comparable<FallbackCondition>
    Represents a FallbackCondition that uses the Convex's class type to determine which pairs will be detected by the fallback NarrowphaseDetector.
